WEBVTT

00:00.009 --> 01:33.848
<font color=<font color="#FCAFF9">C</font><font color="#F1B3F9">o</font><font color="#E7B7F9">p</font><font color="#DCBBF9">y</font><font color="#D2BFF9">r</font><font color="#C7C3F9">i</font><font color="#BDC7F9">g</font><font color="#B2CCFA">h</font><font color="#A8D0FA">t</font><font color="#9DD4FA"> </font><font color="#93D8FA">f</font><font color="#88DCFA">r</font><font color="#7EE0FA">o</font><font color="#73E4FA">m</font><font color="#73E6F1"> </font><font color="#73E8E7">S</font><font color="#73EADE">I</font><font color="#73EBD5"> </font><font color="#73EDCB">M</font><font color="#73EFC2">e</font><font color="#73F1B9">d</font><font color="#73F3AF">i</font><font color="#73F5A6">a</font>

01:33.858 --> 01:36.727
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I always thought
death would be different.</i> </font>

01:36.728 --> 01:40.397
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I expected a great wave of
realization to sweep over me.</i> </font>

01:40.398 --> 01:42.734
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Suddenly, the meaning of life
would be answered along with</i> </font>

01:42.735 --> 01:44.901
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>every other question
I ever had.</i> </font>

01:44.902 --> 01:46.704
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>But there was
nothing to realize.</i> </font>

01:46.705 --> 01:48.372
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I was dead.</i> </font>

01:48.373 --> 01:51.040
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- What?!
- Are you Sheryl Phillips?</font>

01:51.041 --> 01:53.644
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">What, did I forget to put my
trash bins away or something?</font>

01:53.645 --> 01:55.679
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No, ma'am. Your son has died.</font>

01:55.680 --> 01:58.515
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">His body was found in the school
parking lot this morning.</font>

01:58.516 --> 02:00.884
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>A few days ago,</i> </font>

02:00.885 --> 02:03.420
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">right here where I'm standing,
clover high school senior</font>

02:03.421 --> 02:06.423
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Carson Phillips lost his life
when he was struck by lightning.</font>

02:06.424 --> 02:09.493
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">A service will be held this Sunday
at clover community chapel.</font>

02:09.494 --> 02:12.429
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">He will be missed.</font>

02:12.430 --> 02:15.432
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"># It's so hard #</font>

02:15.433 --> 02:19.303
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"># to say goodbye #</font>

02:19.304 --> 02:24.442
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"># to yesterday ##</font>

02:26.443 --> 02:28.445
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>And... My funeral sucks.</i> </font>

02:28.446 --> 02:29.946
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Goodbye, Carson.</font>

02:29.947 --> 02:31.781
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>You've seen my end.</i> </font>

02:31.782 --> 02:34.084
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>But where do I begin?</i> </font>

02:34.085 --> 02:37.688
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I remember when I realized I was
different from everyone else.</i> </font>

02:37.689 --> 02:40.557
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">My name is Carson.
My mom says I was named Carson</font>

02:40.558 --> 02:43.527
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">because that's what was on TV
when I was conceived.</font>

02:43.528 --> 02:46.463
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">When something takes away something
else, what do we call that?</font>

02:46.464 --> 02:48.100
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Not addition, but...
- Homicide.</font>

02:49.100 --> 02:51.435
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I was advanced at a young age.</i> </font>

02:51.436 --> 02:52.969
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Most of the founding fathers</font>

02:52.970 --> 02:55.339
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">were closeted homosexuals
and slave owners.</font>

02:55.340 --> 02:58.075
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>My reports were always
more thorough than my peers.</i> </font>

02:58.076 --> 03:00.042
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'm serious.</font>

03:00.043 --> 03:02.646
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I remember when I discovered
the power of words</i> </font>

03:02.647 --> 03:05.083
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>and how easy it was to escape into
a world of my own by using them.</i> </font>

03:05.084 --> 03:07.650
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>It was a pleasant environment.
Three sheets to the wind, too.</i> </font>

03:07.651 --> 03:10.987
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>You're already.
At least leave me one beer.</i> </font>

03:10.988 --> 03:13.656
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Carson, this is the last time
you'll ever see your grandfather!</font>

03:13.657 --> 03:16.660
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- I know what he looks like!
- Stop fighting me!</font>

03:16.661 --> 03:17.673
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Stand up.</font>

03:21.833 --> 03:23.799
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Boo!
- Ahh!</font>

03:23.800 --> 03:25.935
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">What the hell
is wrong with you?!</font>

03:25.936 --> 03:28.537
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It was lame. I know, I know.</font>

03:28.538 --> 03:30.506
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">The kid's a puss.</font>

03:30.507 --> 03:32.376
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I remember the day
grandma came to live with us.</i> </font>

03:32.377 --> 03:34.845
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Grandma!</font>

03:34.846 --> 03:36.779
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>It's the fifth time
you found her</i> </font>

03:36.780 --> 03:37.849
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>wondering around town.</i> </font>

03:37.850 --> 03:39.683
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Oh, mom.</font>

03:39.684 --> 03:41.585
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">And now
she's in the linen closet.</font>

03:41.586 --> 03:43.686
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Your bedroom is the next door.</font>

03:43.687 --> 03:45.756
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>And the day
that grandma got sick.</i> </font>

03:45.757 --> 03:48.858
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- I wrote you a story, grandma.
- Oh, let's see.</font>

03:48.859 --> 03:53.530
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">"Once upon a time,
there was a boy."</font>

03:53.531 --> 03:55.531
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Well, it could use
a little development,</font>

03:55.532 --> 03:57.400
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">but it's a great beginning.</font>

03:57.401 --> 03:59.070
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>The whole neighborhood
remembers the night</i> </font>

03:59.071 --> 04:01.405
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>that dad left.</i> </font>

04:01.406 --> 04:04.541
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">We just started going back to counseling.
You can't just do this.</font>

04:04.542 --> 04:06.411
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yeah, well, I'm leaving.
I can't take this.</font>

04:06.412 --> 04:08.879
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Where are you going?!
- Anywhere but here.</font>

04:08.880 --> 04:11.715
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- That's mine!
- That is not yours.</font>

04:11.716 --> 04:13.716
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I...Thank you.</font>

04:13.717 --> 04:15.552
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You can't come back!</font>

04:15.553 --> 04:16.619
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No!</font>

04:16.620 --> 04:18.021
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I hate you!</font>

04:18.022 --> 04:20.856
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I hate you!</i> </font>

04:20.857 --> 04:22.726
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Screw it.</font>

04:22.727 --> 04:25.562
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">If anyone asks, we're Jewish.</font>

04:25.563 --> 04:31.067
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>It's been me and mom
ever since.</i> </font>

04:31.068 --> 04:33.437
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Mom, wake up.</font>

04:33.438 --> 04:35.070
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You passed out again.</font>

04:35.071 --> 04:37.707
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Wake up, mom.
- Oh, Jesus!</font>

04:37.708 --> 04:39.942
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Congratulations.
You survived the night.</font>

04:39.943 --> 04:43.914
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Oh, Jesus. If you were descent,
you would just let me sleep.</font>

04:43.915 --> 04:46.750
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">If I was descent,
I'd just put you to sleep.</font>

04:46.751 --> 04:49.786
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">My God. My head.</font>

04:49.787 --> 04:51.887
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You know, the morning
isn't supposed to hurt.</font>

04:51.888 --> 04:53.757
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I don't have to go to school.</font>

04:53.758 --> 04:58.594
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Why do I have to get up?</font>

04:58.595 --> 05:00.163
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Here.</font>

05:00.164 --> 05:01.965
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Are you sure
you're supposed to be drinking</font>

05:01.966 --> 05:04.067
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">with all those pills
Dr. Diehler's giving you?</font>

05:04.068 --> 05:06.604
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Dr. Wheeler. Why don't you just
leave that to the professionals?</font>

05:07.104 --> 05:09.004
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Can I have my other glass
back, please?</font>

05:09.005 --> 05:10.507
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It's in the sink.
Get it yourself.</font>

05:11.107 --> 05:13.844
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You know, you make me wish I'd
had that abortion in the '90s.</font>

05:13.845 --> 05:16.245
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- That makes two of us.
- Go to school already!</font>

05:16.246 --> 05:18.048
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Go! Go! Go!</font>

05:18.049 --> 05:20.216
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">And if I am still sleeping
when you get home,</font>

05:20.217 --> 05:25.622
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">don't you dare put my hand
in a bowl of water again.</font>

05:25.623 --> 05:27.690
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Shut up.</font>

05:27.691 --> 05:28.991
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Bye. Love you, too.</font>

05:29.126 --> 05:31.795
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Would you bring me
my pillow back?!</font>

05:31.796 --> 05:33.964
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Close the shades.</font>

05:33.965 --> 05:36.500
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I hate you.</font>

05:36.501 --> 05:38.502
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>High school.</i> </font>

05:38.503 --> 05:40.770
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Society's bright idea
to put all their aggressive,</i> </font>

05:40.771 --> 05:43.507
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>self righteous, pubescent, naive
youth into one environment</i> </font>

05:43.508 --> 05:45.709
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>to torment and emotionally
scar each other for life.</i> </font>

05:46.109 --> 05:50.147
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Cattle, cattle, cattle, cattle!</font>

05:52.148 --> 05:56.519
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Shakespeare once wrote
that life is but a dream.</i> </font>

05:56.520 --> 05:58.988
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>And that's exactly
how I lived my life,</i> </font>

05:58.989 --> 06:01.190
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>from one dream to the next.</i> </font>

06:01.191 --> 06:04.094
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Hating every update of reality.</i> </font>

06:04.095 --> 06:07.264
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Well, the "I" stands for
an imaginary number.</font>

06:07.265 --> 06:09.866
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay, hold up. There are
imaginary numbers now?</font>

06:09.867 --> 06:12.736
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Are there unicorns the next lesson?
Can someone please</font>

06:12.737 --> 06:16.072
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">teach me something useful,
like how to balance a checkbook?</font>

06:16.073 --> 06:18.675
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.
Why did I get a "c" on this?</font>

06:18.676 --> 06:21.011
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- This is a great paper.
- The assignment was to pick</font>

06:21.012 --> 06:23.680
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">either evolution or creationism
and provide background evidence</font>

06:23.681 --> 06:25.682
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">as to why
you believe that theory.</font>

06:25.683 --> 06:28.017
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I know. I picked evolution.</font>

06:28.018 --> 06:30.954
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I said that it's obvious creatures
can adapt to their environments</font>

06:30.955 --> 06:33.557
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">because I no longer
have the urge to throw things</font>

06:33.558 --> 06:36.026
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">at students
who believe in creationism.</font>

06:36.027 --> 06:37.861
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Right?</font>

06:37.862 --> 06:39.161
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Right?</font>

06:39.162 --> 06:42.031
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I believe in creationism.</font>

06:42.032 --> 06:43.933
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Exhibit "a."</font>

06:43.934 --> 06:45.903
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Welcome to career day
here at the counseling center.</font>

06:45.904 --> 06:48.070
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Right, I'm sure
you saw our flier.</font>

06:48.071 --> 06:50.574
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">And you know, we're here to
just sort of help you kiddos</font>

06:50.575 --> 06:54.144
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">establish your future career
options, what do you want to do...</font>

06:54.145 --> 06:56.178
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I know the exact career
that I want.</font>

06:56.179 --> 06:57.947
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. What is it, munchkin?</font>

06:57.948 --> 06:59.917
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I want to be the editor
of the New Yorker</i> </font>

06:59.918 --> 07:02.685
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and the youngest freelance
journalist to be published</font>

07:02.686 --> 07:04.355
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>in the New York times, LA times, Boston
herald, and the Chicago tribune.</i> </font>

07:04.356 --> 07:06.890
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You have had some time
to think about this then, huh?</font>

07:06.891 --> 07:10.594
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Every day since I was eight.
- Okay. Well...</font>

07:10.595 --> 07:14.331
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">What about college? I can help you
decide what college to go to.</font>

07:14.332 --> 07:16.700
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Uh, no. I've got
to get into Northwestern.</font>

07:16.701 --> 07:19.002
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">All right.
Where is that exactly?</font>

07:19.003 --> 07:21.837
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Illinois.
- Never heard of it.</font>

07:21.838 --> 07:25.675
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I've put 17 good years
into this town, okay?</font>

07:25.676 --> 07:27.945
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">People spend less time
in prison for murder sentences.</font>

07:27.946 --> 07:30.079
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Is that true?
- Yes. Yes, look it up.</font>

07:30.080 --> 07:32.248
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I've been the president
of the writers' club</font>

07:32.249 --> 07:34.617
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and the editor of the newspaper
since sophomore year</font>

07:34.618 --> 07:36.953
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">just to better my chances
of getting into that school.</font>

07:36.954 --> 07:39.089
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">That is so smart.</font>

07:39.090 --> 07:42.091
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Wow.
- It's been challenging.</font>

07:42.092 --> 07:45.829
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">So I've already applied
and I meet all the requirements.</font>

07:45.830 --> 07:48.697
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I just haven't
heard back from them.</font>

07:48.698 --> 07:50.800
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">So I'd appreciate it if you um,</font>

07:50.801 --> 07:52.104
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">maybe found out why.</font>

07:53.104 --> 07:56.772
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. And that is something that I would do?
I would call them?</font>

07:56.773 --> 07:58.375
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Yes.
- Okay.</font>

07:58.376 --> 08:00.944
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I will do anything
to get into that school.</font>

08:00.945 --> 08:02.214
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- I mean anything.
- I'm on it.</font>

08:03.114 --> 08:05.949
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">But since you're here,
how 'bout you just fill out this</font>

08:05.950 --> 08:08.284
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">clover community college
application.</font>

08:08.285 --> 08:10.053
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">'Cause with every application,</font>

08:10.054 --> 08:11.423
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I get a point
towards a juice cup.</font>

08:12.123 --> 08:13.957
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Ahem. Do you juice?</font>

08:13.958 --> 08:15.626
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Because it's really
changed how I feel.</font>

08:16.126 --> 08:18.795
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Last week's edition of
the clover high chronicle</i> </font>

08:18.796 --> 08:21.264
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">was yet another disappointment.</font>

08:21.265 --> 08:24.300
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">We did have new material
for each of the sections,</font>

08:24.301 --> 08:29.673
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">but once again, it was
all written by me.</font>

08:29.674 --> 08:32.741
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Now this, this has to stop.</font>

08:32.741 --> 08:35.208
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>This is not the
Carson Phillips chronicle.</i> </font>

08:35.210 --> 08:37.681
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>All right? It's the
clover high chronicle.</i> </font>

08:37.682 --> 08:40.015
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Carson Phillips. Clover high.</font>

08:40.017 --> 08:43.018
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hopefully,
this week will be different.</font>

08:43.019 --> 08:47.257
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Dwayne! Do you have that movie
review ready for manslaughter 3 yet?</i> </font>

08:47.258 --> 08:48.724
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Yes.
- Yeah?</font>

08:48.725 --> 08:50.259
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- No.
- No.</font>

08:50.260 --> 08:51.994
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I went, but I passed out.</font>

08:51.995 --> 08:53.431
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You didn't tell me
it was gonna be in 3d.</font>

08:53.432 --> 08:55.931
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- It wasn't.
- Whoa.</font>

08:55.932 --> 08:59.169
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Vicki. Do you have
your weather report ready?</font>

08:59.170 --> 09:03.342
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- What?
- Your weather report.</font>

09:06.343 --> 09:09.713
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yeah, it's cloudy.</font>

09:09.714 --> 09:11.848
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. Thank you, Vicki.</font>

09:11.849 --> 09:13.282
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Progress, right?</font>

09:13.283 --> 09:16.319
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">And uh, Emilio,</font>

09:16.320 --> 09:19.922
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">do you have a section
you'd like to tackle this week?</font>

09:19.923 --> 09:23.959
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Uh... I love America.</font>

