29:01.036 --> 29:02.506
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">ripped them up
into little pieces</font>

29:03.106 --> 29:04.973
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and threw 'em
into the fireplace.</font>

29:04.974 --> 29:06.908
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I forget.</font>

29:06.909 --> 29:09.211
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I have to talk to you!</font>

29:09.212 --> 29:11.045
