29:11.046 --> 29:13.214
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'm tired.</font>

29:13.215 --> 29:15.550
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">What do you need, Mr. Phillips?</font>

29:15.551 --> 29:18.986
