29:25.395 --> 29:28.397
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Uh, God!</font>

29:28.398 --> 29:31.066
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I...</font>

29:31.067 --> 29:33.936
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I want to start
a school literary magazine.</font>

29:36.238 --> 29:38.406
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Why... why are you laughing?</font>

29:38.407 --> 29:41.076
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay, fine.</font>

29:41.077 --> 29:45.246
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You can start your
literary magazine or you know,</font>

29:45.247 --> 29:48.582
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">you can start a hunting
magazine for all I care,</font>

29:48.583 --> 29:50.484
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">but...</font>

29:50.485 --> 29:53.422
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You're gonna have to find
your own funding because...</font>

29:53.423 --> 29:55.957
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">The school is broke.</font>

29:55.958 --> 29:59.027
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'd also like to announce it
