29:59.028 --> 30:01.195
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It'll take three seconds.</font>

30:01.196 --> 30:04.232
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Fine. If for nothing else
