30:04.233 --> 30:06.635
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Great. Great. Thank you.</font>

30:06.636 --> 30:10.272
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

30:10.273 --> 30:15.609
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hey! Break it up!
