30:21.617 --> 30:24.418
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I got ya! I got ya! I got ya!</font>

30:24.419 --> 30:26.288
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yep, that's it.</font>

30:26.289 --> 30:27.523
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yep, it's just papers.</font>

30:28.123 --> 30:32.462
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Signature
