30:36.131 --> 30:41.470
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. Yeah, thanks, Sheryl.</font>

30:41.471 --> 30:43.571
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">For what's it's worth,
I'm sorry.</font>

30:43.572 --> 30:46.008
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'm sorry I'm not the man
you wanted me to be.</font>

30:46.009 --> 30:48.210
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Yeah. Me, too.
