30:48.211 --> 30:49.477
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay.</font>

30:49.478 --> 30:51.312
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Oh, please. Please, please.</font>

30:51.313 --> 30:53.913
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. I'll see ya.</font>

31:01.358 --> 31:03.958
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. I'll see ya.</font>

31:11.667 --> 31:14.168
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>There's so much stress
in my life.</i> </font>

31:14.169 --> 31:17.772
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It's a miracle I'm able to
