31:17.773 --> 31:20.274
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">But does anybody care?</font>

31:20.275 --> 31:22.210
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Does anybody...</font>

31:22.211 --> 31:24.513
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Does my son see how much I
struggle every single day?</font>

31:24.514 --> 31:27.515
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Well, I don't envy you.
