31:27.516 --> 31:30.351
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You're the only person
who understands my situation.</font>

31:30.352 --> 31:33.221
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">He's becoming more and more
