31:33.222 --> 31:35.089
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">He's rude, sarcastic.</font>

31:35.090 --> 31:37.525
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">He makes a joke at my
