31:42.586 --> 31:43.697
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">If I had a goldfish...</font>

31:43.698 --> 31:46.268
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">He would probably
abandon you as well.</font>

31:46.269 --> 31:48.837
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- It would abandon me.
- But you don't have a goldfish.</font>

31:48.838 --> 31:51.072
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No, I don't, thank God.</font>

31:51.073 --> 31:53.140
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Well, the thing
about goldfish is</font>

31:53.141 --> 31:55.577
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">they're in that bowl,
