31:55.578 --> 31:58.213
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It would find a way.</font>

31:58.214 --> 32:00.714
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">That's pretty extreme thinking.</font>

32:00.715 --> 32:03.585
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Um, let me ask you this.
- Yes.</font>

32:03.586 --> 32:06.387
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Is he on antidepressants?
- No.</font>

32:06.388 --> 32:09.191
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Do you think he needs them?
- Do I think he needs them?</font>

32:09.192 --> 32:11.225
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Well, in all honesty,</font>

32:11.226 --> 32:13.561
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I think all teenagers need them</font>

32:13.562 --> 32:15.830
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">whether they're
depressed or not.</font>

32:15.831 --> 32:17.866
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You know, teenagers
are so full of hormones.</font>

32:17.867 --> 32:20.268
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">They don't know
what the hell they want.</font>

32:20.269 --> 32:23.006
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">All they're thinking about is rubbing
against a pillow or a cushion</font>

32:23.106 --> 32:24.608
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">or another teenager.
You know, so.</font>

32:25.108 --> 32:27.577
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I can't believe how you're
making me feel so much better.</font>

32:27.578 --> 32:30.412
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">And I think if he had
something to ground him,</font>

32:30.413 --> 32:34.551
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">uh, he wouldn't be
so eager to fly away.</font>

32:36.552 --> 32:41.255
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You need to be
on antidepressants.</font>

32:41.256 --> 32:42.791
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No way.</font>

32:42.792 --> 32:44.859
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You're medicated enough
for the both of us.</font>

32:44.860 --> 32:46.695
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Aren't you depressed?</font>

32:46.696 --> 32:49.731
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Currently, while having
this conversation? Yeah.</font>

32:49.732 --> 32:51.765
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Everyone gets depressed.</font>

32:51.766 --> 32:53.666
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It's an emotion.
People turn to pills.</font>

32:53.667 --> 32:55.638
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Before they turn
to their problems these days.</font>

32:55.639 --> 32:58.339
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Well, sometimes
it's the only solution.</font>

32:58.340 --> 33:00.876
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You're depressing me right now.
Are you saying that</font>

33:00.877 --> 33:03.279
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'm gonna take a pill
and then you're gonna disappear?</font>

33:03.280 --> 33:04.713
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">That was uncalled for.</font>

33:04.714 --> 33:06.781
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">And so are
most prescription drugs.</font>

33:06.782 --> 33:09.283
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">We are living in
