33:09.284 --> 33:12.620
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">We start drugging kids with
A.D.D., which they all have,</font>

33:12.621 --> 33:15.156
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and then it
doesn't stop till death.</font>

33:15.157 --> 33:17.627
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">You were on add medication
as a kid, and you turned out</font>

33:17.628 --> 33:19.461
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">somewhat decent.</font>

33:19.462 --> 33:21.229
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No, I wasn't.</font>

33:21.230 --> 33:24.302
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I hid it in your food.</font>

33:28.303 --> 33:30.773
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I thought I was just really
calm and mature for my age.</font>

33:30.774 --> 33:32.573
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Nope, you were drugged.</font>

33:32.574 --> 33:35.277
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">When your father and I
started our divorce,</font>

33:35.278 --> 33:37.647
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">you started asking so many
questions, we found it easier</font>

33:37.648 --> 33:43.185
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">to roofie you than answer you.</font>

33:43.186 --> 33:45.486
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Well, it isn't dinner
unless some form of</font>

33:45.487 --> 33:47.490
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">my childhood foundation
