33:50.960 --> 33:53.662
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I need more money. $300.</font>

33:53.663 --> 33:56.330
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I want to start
a literary magazine at school,</font>

33:56.331 --> 33:59.466
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and I need money to print
the first 100 copies or so.</font>

33:59.467 --> 34:01.235
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No.</font>

34:01.236 --> 34:02.368
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Why not?
I know you're rolling in it.</font>

34:02.369 --> 34:03.673
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Grandpa died
