34:03.674 --> 34:06.608
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Wrong. He left me everything.
You, his car.</font>

34:06.609 --> 34:09.878
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- What about my college fund?
- Key word, college.</font>

34:09.879 --> 34:15.516
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. If I start
taking antidepressants,</font>

34:15.518 --> 34:20.225
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">will you give me the money
to start my literary magazine?</font>

34:23.226 --> 34:24.458
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Deal.</font>

34:24.460 --> 34:26.293
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Pass me the salt.</font>

34:26.295 --> 34:28.696
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hello,
future farmers and inmates.</font>

34:28.697 --> 34:31.533
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I'm Carson Phillips from
the clover high chronicle</i> </font>

34:31.534 --> 34:34.534
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">here with some
very exciting news.</font>

34:34.536 --> 34:37.539
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">This year,
for the first time ever,</font>

34:37.540 --> 34:41.309
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">clover high will release its
