34:41.310 --> 34:44.380
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Whoo! Awesome!</font>

34:46.248 --> 34:49.882
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Now, I know most of you
can't read let alone write,</font>

34:49.884 --> 34:52.553
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">but for all
