34:58.594 --> 35:01.896
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Poems. Short stories.</i> </font>

35:01.897 --> 35:04.399
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Hit lists.</i> </font>

35:04.400 --> 35:05.899
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Anything.</font>

35:05.900 --> 35:08.570
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. Thank you.</font>

35:08.571 --> 35:09.803
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">God bless.</font>

35:09.804 --> 35:11.804
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Whoo! Carson!</font>

35:16.279 --> 35:19.280
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay, assembly dismissed.
