<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Oh... No.</font>

35:42.438 --> 35:44.939
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Shiterary magazine.</font>

35:44.940 --> 35:47.408
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">God.</font>

35:47.409 --> 35:49.510
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Typical. I mean,</font>

