36:06.328 --> 36:10.798
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">If you can get Nicholas Forbes</font>

36:10.799 --> 36:13.801
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>and Scott Thomas
