<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Each other...</font>

36:36.991 --> 36:39.361
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">In the boy's locker room.</font>

36:39.362 --> 36:42.564
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I just go in there
