36:47.103 --> 36:49.704
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Oh, that must be awkward.</font>

36:49.705 --> 36:51.506
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Too bad they aren't writers.</font>

36:51.507 --> 36:53.742
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">If they had work
