37:06.621 --> 37:09.022
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Even Claire Mathews.</font>

37:09.023 --> 37:11.024
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Ha!</font>

37:11.025 --> 37:12.526
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yeah.</font>

37:12.527 --> 37:16.527
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yeah, I guess you're right.</font>

37:20.536 --> 37:22.137
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I travel lightly today.</font>

37:22.138 --> 37:24.138
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Not a problem, Mrs. Phillips.</font>

37:24.139 --> 37:28.876
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Ms. Ms. Ms.</font>

37:28.877 --> 37:30.544
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">What?</font>

37:30.545 --> 37:32.046
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Why are you looking at me</font>

37:32.047 --> 37:33.949
