37:51.500 --> 37:57.171
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Neal Phillips?</font>

37:57.172 --> 37:59.908
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Wait! Miss Phillips?</font>

37:59.909 --> 38:02.777
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Sheryl?!</font>

38:05.581 --> 38:06.281
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hi.</font>

38:09.752 --> 38:11.051
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hi.</font>

38:11.052 --> 38:13.086
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">How was work?</font>

38:13.087 --> 38:14.988
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Not good.</font>

38:14.989 --> 38:17.926
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'm sorry, but there's
