50:30.759 --> 50:32.826
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Excuse me.</font>

50:37.331 --> 50:39.733
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I'm worried most of you</font>

50:39.734 --> 50:43.803
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">have taken one too many
