51:04.826 --> 51:07.760
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I like the color green.</i> </font>

51:07.761 --> 51:10.964
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>When I see green,
