51:10.965 --> 51:14.702
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>and grass.</i> </font>

51:14.703 --> 51:17.638
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>When I think of grass,
