51:17.639 --> 51:19.872
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>- Brilliant.
- We can't cheer</i> </font>

51:19.873 --> 51:21.874
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">if we're not cultured.</font>

51:21.875 --> 51:24.711
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I just want everyone
