51:30.784 --> 51:32.885
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I love cheerleading.</i> </font>

51:32.886 --> 51:35.722
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>But the worst thing about
