51:43.598 --> 51:45.633
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>where innocence was rare</i> </font>

51:45.634 --> 51:49.903
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>and so were the living.</i> </font>

51:49.904 --> 51:53.274
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Why do people live
