52:16.531 --> 52:20.466
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>it's a premonition.</i> </font>

52:20.467 --> 52:22.368
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Roses are red,</i> </font>

52:22.369 --> 52:24.338
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>violets are blue,</i> </font>

52:24.339 --> 52:28.843
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>no amount of money
could keep me away from you.</i> </font>

52:30.844 --> 52:32.946
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>There was
once a little princess</i> </font>

52:32.947 --> 52:34.882
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>with several responsibilities.</i> </font>

52:34.883 --> 52:37.318
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Her parents,
the king and queen,</i> </font>

52:37.319 --> 52:39.054
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>put way too much
pressure on her</i> </font>

52:39.055 --> 52:43.959
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>since they had troubles
managing the kingdom.</i> </font>

52:46.960 --> 52:49.963
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Malerie writing</i> </font>

52:49.964 --> 52:53.334
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>part 38.</i> </font>

52:53.335 --> 52:56.803
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Action.</i> </font>

52:56.804 --> 52:58.472
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>Call me...</i> </font>

52:58.473 --> 53:00.807
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Isabella.</font>

53:00.808 --> 53:04.945
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It's genius.</font>

53:04.946 --> 53:07.647
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>It was anything like
