53:07.648 --> 53:09.551
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>For the first time in my life,</i> </font>

53:09.552 --> 53:11.517
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I was winning.</i> </font>

53:11.518 --> 53:13.822
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>For the first time,
everything seemed reachable.</i> </font>

53:13.823 --> 53:17.827
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It's like Christmas.</font>

53:20.828 --> 53:24.765
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">So I'm blackmailing
the entire school</font>

53:24.766 --> 53:27.501
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">to better my chances
of getting into the university</font>

53:27.502 --> 53:30.370
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">of my dreams,
and it's exhilarating.</font>

53:30.371 --> 53:32.372
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I mean,
who'd of thought that one of</font>

53:32.373 --> 53:36.843
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">my biggest accomplishments
