53:36.844 --> 53:39.012
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Get out.
- Oh, no,</font>

53:39.013 --> 53:41.080
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">not today, grandma.
