53:41.081 --> 53:43.684
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- Not today.
- Get out.</font>

53:43.685 --> 53:45.753
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Get out. I do not know you!</font>

53:45.754 --> 53:48.055
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">All right, okay, I'm leaving.</font>

53:48.056 --> 53:50.990
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>So we still need a venue
