54:00.034 --> 54:01.801
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">No objections.</font>

54:01.802 --> 54:03.570
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Isn't quail gardens</font>

54:03.571 --> 54:05.705
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">like right in the middle
