54:24.726 --> 54:27.428
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Oh, my God. I love Rapunzel.</font>

54:27.429 --> 54:29.896
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yeah, I'm not sure
