<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">'20s is fine.</font>

54:41.743 --> 54:43.776
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Super.</font>

54:43.777 --> 54:46.446
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Okay. Why are you guys, uh,</font>

54:46.447 --> 54:48.849
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">letting me make
