55:02.764 --> 55:04.932
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">just bills and ads</font>

55:04.933 --> 55:06.101
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and bills, bills, bills.</font>

55:07.101 --> 55:08.103
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Let me see.</font>

55:09.103 --> 55:10.937
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Magazines...</font>

55:10.938 --> 55:13.539
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Uh, let me know
