<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">It's... My dad.</font>

56:55.710 --> 56:56.876
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hello?</font>

56:56.877 --> 56:58.112
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Hey, Carson.</font>

56:59.112 --> 57:01.181
