58:06.179 --> 58:08.280
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Have fun.</font>

58:08.281 --> 58:10.783
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Be home at a decent hour and,</font>

