59:48.116 --> 59:50.850
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">- And you left me with her.
- Carson...</font>

59:50.851 --> 59:52.419
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Yeah, you know, I can't...</font>

59:52.420 --> 59:54.221
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">Thank you, April.
