01:04:37.505 --> 01:04:39.772
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">and others don't?</font>

01:04:39.773 --> 01:04:43.110
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">I mean, why do
