01:05:01.061 --> 01:05:04.229
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00">A scarf blanket.</font>

01:05:04.230 --> 01:05:06.399
<font face="Microsoft Sans Serif" color="#ffff00"> <i>I wanted to be heard so bad</i> </font>

